子亚当、内特、卢克和克里斯，以及他的许多朋友和同事。」"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-c05d136600e5cde94579590632e65d4b_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "43 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/657384235"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I2Mb05f3xsNVwEAMaCTEwODM2MzI3MCCEmtOyBjAAOCRAIXIJNjU3Mzg0MjM1eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "34_1716905867.281386", "card_id": "Q_33752494", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 46}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么看了《喜剧之王》最后是圆满的结局我却一点也高兴不起来？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "周星驰"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-922054fb44ee42d338c4f9b18c724c14_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "43 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/33752494"}}, "attached_info": "Cj0I2Mb05f3xsNVwEAMaBzU3MDc2NTggydPvrQUwADjJAUAicggzMzc1MjQ5NHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "35_1716905867.281892", "card_id": "Q_657024888", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 126}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "你的通勤时间是多久，你觉得值得吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "大城市通勤的你，有没有动辄来回四个小时的通勤时间，(8 小时工作时间，加上 4 小时通勤，平平常常超过 12 小时) 相比小城市半个小时的圈子，你有什么感想？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-bbf97449f9a22d4d35d4535a469416f1_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "43 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/657024888"}}, "attached_info": "CkAI2Mb05f3xsNVwEAMaCTEwODI4MzM2OSCc+cCyBjAAOLQBQCNyCTY1NzAyNDg4OHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_ty